Load Public API Distribution

Source: R/catalog_main.R
public_temporal.Rd

Load Public API Distribution

Usage

public_temporal(dataset, fname = TRUE)

Arguments

dataset

<chr> dataset title

fname

<lgl> Is dataset a function name?; default is TRUE

Value

<Distribution> object

Examples

public_temporal("utilization_provider")
#> ══ Medicare Physician & Other Practitioners - by Provider ══
#> 
#> ☰ Rows 1,230,293 ☰ Fields 82 ☰ Pages 247 ☰ Resources 4 ☰
#> 
#>   The Medicare Physician & Other Practitioners by Provider
#>   dataset provides information on use, payments, submitted
#>   charges and beneficiary demographic and health
#>   characteristics organized by National Provider Identifier
#>   (NPI). Note: This full dataset contains more records than
#>   most spreadsheet programs can handle, which will result
#>   in an incomplete load of data. Use of a database or
#>   statistical software is required.
#> 
#> • Timespan ❯ 2013-01-01 - 2022-12-31
#> • Released ❯ Annually [R/P1Y]
#> • Modified ❯ 2024-06-04
#> 
#> ℹ Data Dictionary | Landing Page | References

public_temporal("quality_payment")
#> ══ Quality Payment Program Experience ══════════════════════
#> 
#> ☰ Rows 624,200 ☰ Fields 165 ☰ Pages 125 ☰ Resources 3 ☰
#> 
#>   The Quality Payment Program (QPP) Experience dataset
#>   provides participation and performance information in the
#>   Merit-based Incentive Payment System (MIPS) during each
#>   performance year. They cover eligibility and
#>   participation, performance categories, and final score
#>   and payment adjustments. The dataset provides additional
#>   details at the TIN/NPI level on what was published in the
#>   previous performance year. You can sort the data by
#>   variables like clinician type, practice size, scores, and
#>   payment adjustments.
#> 
#> • Timespan ❯ 2017-01-01 - 2022-12-31
#> • Released ❯ Annually [R/P1Y]
#> • Modified ❯ 2024-05-08
#>
